article_title: As ObamaCare Launches, Walgreen Profit Soars

article_metadata.description: Walgreen Co., the giant pharmacy that is pushing more into providing health care services beyond the prescription counter, said its first quarter profits jumped 68 percent. The jump in profits to $695 million, or 72 cents a share in the quarter ended Nov. 30 compares to $413 million, or 43 cents [...]
